TC01: SELECT avg(D1.noFailedDLSessionsT1) AS DL_FAILEDSESSIONS_T1 FROM (SELECT DATE_ID AS DATE_ID,HOUR_ID AS HOUR_ID,NR_NAME AS NR_NAME,NRCellDU AS NRCellDU,SN AS SN,SUM( case when DCVECTOR_INDEX <= 1 then pmEbsnMacDrbThpDlMbbLowVolDistr else 0 end ) as noFailedDLSessionsT1 FROM DC_E_NR_EVENTS_NRCELLDU_V_RAW DA WHERE DA.DATE_ID >= @date AND DA.ROWSTATUS NOT IN ('DUPLICATE', 'SUSPECTED') AND DA.DCVECTOR_INDEX <= 26 GROUP BY DA.DATE_ID, DA.HOUR_ID, DA.NR_NAME, DA.NRCellDU, DA.SN ) AS D1
